Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.13,0:00:09.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:53.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:58.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:27.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to move on to\Nthe next phase of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:42.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't lose face in the high council.\NChor Tempest can't go on as it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:56.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until the repairs on the Arcus Prima\Nare completed, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:02.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will board the Messis and be\Ncharged with border reconnaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? We're boarding that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable. You should\Njust be thankful Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's right.\NThat old boat should do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Birds in a Cage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:04.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, are we really\Ngonna live here, all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:08.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, you'd better save your\Ncomplaining till you've secured a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:12.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The beds on the window side\Nare first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Best regards, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Best regards, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:35.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, do you think we'll\Nbe living here for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just like we can't\Nchange what's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's no telling\Nwhat's in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You may be right about that, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, where's Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We believe the damage\Nwas caused in transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:12.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,The communication-wire\Nejectors have come a bit loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you manage\Nwithout replacing parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:21.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,There'll be a severe shortage of\Nreplacement parts. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're having\Na hard time, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not compared to\Nyou sibyllae. You're all so noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything must seem new to you...\NI'm sure you're taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:38.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Noble you say? We can't afford\Nto worry about being noble right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as you can\Nfly a Simoun, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:57.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then that's how I'd like\Nthe reconnaissance tasks divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NBut if I may, Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:08.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the finest chor and\Nthe pride of Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:13.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Though my crew and I are\Ngreatly honored by your presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...why were you assigned\Nto an old front-line vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, the inconvenience\Nis written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter. You're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:31.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And someone from a different chain\Nof command is invading your bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well, Sibylla Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:38.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will refrain from\Nasking you anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, please stop... Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's beneath you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:54.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've worked in\Nkitchens since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really enjoy doing this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:46.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,This area along the Shoukoku border\Nis most vulnerable to invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,This may be a scheduled recon\Nflight, but don't drop your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Scheduled recon flight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NWhen Simoun sibyllae take to the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Simoun sibyllae take to the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she is "praying to the skies."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Controlling a Simoun is\N"speaking with a Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, we took off to speak with\Nour Simouns and pray to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:16.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're to be back at base at noon.\NTill then, don't forget to be vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a mouse! A mouse, a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean there are mice on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I grew up on a farm,\Nso there were lots of mice around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, the same goes\Nfor you. Right, Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,So far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can really get\Non your nerves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, let's head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, they're too far away to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'd be wiser to return\Nand make our report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't stand living in a room like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:28.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does Dominüra get\Nher own room? It's definitely fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to Dominüra's pleading\Nthat we were able to board this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of hearing your\Nwhining and complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aer...\NIs it true that mice bite people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,So they do bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:30.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,We spotted far off what we\Nbelieved to be enemy planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they noticed us,\Nthey fled immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,They were so far\Nwe lost them in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should report to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, the acting captain is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:50.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've explained my position.\NWould you like to hear it again, Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest's regina is Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:59.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra is the mediator\Nbetween our chor and Wauf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the patrol ship Messis's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Chor Tempest comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta,\Nmake your report to Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everybody! Lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard Mamina made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You seem sad, Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI'm feeling very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:45.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, Anubituf, I was sure\Nthat you'd be feeling the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:52.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest,\Nthose glorious Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're the ones\Nwho took away that glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, I'll save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:04.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I shall do everything in my\Npower to summon them back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:12.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it really in their best interests to be\Ncalled back to the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even I can't answer that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!\NSmells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making me all warm inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty,\Nso you can have seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, aren't you eating too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:09.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened the other day... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:15.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's pretend the whole thing never\Nhappened. Is that clear, Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey,\Nwhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so mean.\NYou could at least tell us, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you\Nafter lunch if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The new sibylla made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:24.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're pretty late for someone\Nwho called me here, Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,On a puny boat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NWhat did you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't say anything...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come now, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that I didn't\Nhave any feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can I patch things up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:17.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Patch things up? That sounds\Nlike we were actually friends before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:22.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Till the end, one of us will always\Nbe above and the other below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just what were\Nyou thinking that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I wanted to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I feel the same way even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,This conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always envious\Nof those braids of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,But these are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:49.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,You plait your hair because\Nyour parents told you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:54.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those things don't mean\Na thing to a child. To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they were a rich girl's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:20.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the chor all Simoun\Nsibyllae worship and take pride in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:23.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the finest chor of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,On behalf of all Simoun sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I beg you to consider\Npreserving Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:34.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you mean\NChor Tempest as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or Chor Tempest as\Na squadron of warriors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:44.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say you want us to preserve\NChor Tempest, but which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Twelve sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:51.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who become each other's pairs\Nand draw Ri Majons across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is only one Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:00.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were there that day\Nas well, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:06.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard everything that\Nwent on during that hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Vura and Onasia, Chor\NTempest was saved from disbanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was also due to your\Nbrilliant speech, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:21.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am not looking to blame\Nanyone for this war we're waging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how tragic and painful it\Nis now, I believe it was meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:30.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether or not that is\NTempus Spatium's will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes no difference to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:38.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer even care whether\Nit's God's will anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, I do have\None question for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite all this, can I still\Ncall myself a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:53.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you overheard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:01.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I'd like you to select\Nthe next sibyllae to go on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, next will be two pairs,\Nyou and Rimone, Alty and Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:15.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The truth is you're the one\Nwho saved Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You negotiated with the council\Nto keep us, provided we be sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to the front lines\Non this ship, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:27.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the greatest\Nchor in Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, how can you do such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's pretty neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a keepsake from my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:25.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell me the enemy's\Nbehavior in this morning's patrol again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine... But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:32.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you sighted distant traces\Nof the enemy several times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and they immediately fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,We encountered them\Nthree times to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:44.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you four\Nreally saw them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:50.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they spotted us first and\Nrevealed themselves on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most likely. Paraietta, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll notify the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest of you,\Nhurry to the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Neviril.\NIt never occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your scouting flight\Npath has been tracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra and the others are being\Nambushed. We're at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're at the front lines\Nof the enemy's assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina and\NRoatreamon aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the auriga.\NKaim, please pair with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, you're my sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.\NGet a move on, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:37.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll send Mamina and Roatreamon\Nas soon as they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What will you do,\NSibylla Roatreamon, Sibylla Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The others have already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not going to pair\Nwith you! Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over my dead body.\NIt's never going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:23.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-What... What do you\Nthink you're doing, Roatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You called me that\Nwhen we were little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:36.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in danger...\NThey could all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:43.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no time for us\Nto be hesitating, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Roatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Emergency positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still sniveling?\NWe're on our way to meet the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it... That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that I've always,\Nalways worn braids...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:51.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!\NWe can take on that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,That meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:46.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:51.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:58.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:06.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:23.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:37.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:43.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.49,0:23:46.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:59.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:05.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's our job as sibyllae\Nto take the soldiers near that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:14.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:15.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,United Front\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:18.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,United Front\NUnited Front.
